{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/tech/2020/01/06/修复Windows下打开Jupyter时报NotImplementError.html","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"宫不上叔"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"1249d160-9182-5b1b-9ef3-bcdf60ed4d87","excerpt":"修复Windows下打开Jupyter报NotImplementError 打开. 修改 改为如下","html":"<h1>修复Windows下打开Jupyter报NotImplementError</h1>\n<p>打开<code class=\"language-text\">/c/Users/{USER_NAME}/AppData/Local/Programs/Python/Python38/Lib/asyncio/__init__/py</code>.</p>\n<p>修改</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> sys<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>platform <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token string\">'win32'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>windows_event <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>\n    __all__ <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> windows_events<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>__all__</code></pre></div>\n<p>改为如下</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> asyncio\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> sys<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>platform <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token string\">'win32'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>windows_event <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>\n    asyncio<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>set_event_loop_policy<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>asyncio<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>WindowsSelectorEventLoopPolicy<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    __all__ <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> windows_events<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>__all__</code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"category":"tech"},"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2020/01/06/修复Windows下打开Jupyter时报NotImplementError.html","date":"January 06, 2020","title":"修复Windows下打开Jupyter时报NotImplementError"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/tech/2020/01/06/修复Windows下打开Jupyter时报NotImplementError.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2020/01/05/利用CloudFlare实现网站https访问.html","title":"利用CloudFlare实现网站https访问"},"frontmatter":{"category":"tech"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/life/2020/01/12/歌舞剧「巴黎圣母院」.html","title":"歌舞剧「巴黎圣母院」"},"frontmatter":{"category":"life"}}}}}